History
-------

Early versions of the kuso CLI (pre-v0.6.0) descended from
kubero-cli (https://github.com/kubero-dev/kubero-cli), licensed
under GPL-3.0. As of v0.6.0, all CLI source files have been
rewritten clean-room and the operator + server + web frontend
are independent works.
